"and additional keywords to describe programmes. This option will retrieve "
"this additional information. This can be very detailed (20+ actors per "
"movie) and will take a lot of memory and resources on this box, and will "
"pass this information to your client machines and GUI too, using memory and "
"resources on those boxes too. Do not enable on low-spec machines."
msgstr ""
"Obtain 列表 of credits (actors, etc.), keywords and extra 信息 from the xml 标签 "
"(if 可用). Some xmltv providers supply a 列表 of actors and additional keywords "
"to describe programmes. This 选项 will retrieve this additional 信息. This can "
"be very detailed (20+ actors per movie) and will take a lot of memory and "
"resources on this box, and will pass this 信息 to your 客户端 machines and GUI "
"too, using memory and resources on those boxes too. Do not 启用 on low-spec "
"machines."

