#: src/epggrab.c:425
msgid ""
"Writes the current in-memory EPG database to disk every x hours, so should a"
" crash/unexpected shutdown occur EPG data is saved periodically to the "
"database (re-read on next startup). Set to 0 to disable."
msgstr ""
"Writes the 当前 in-memory EPG database to disk every x hours, so should a "
"crash/unexpected shutdown occur EPG 数据 is saved periodically to the database"
" (re-read on 下一个 startup). Set to 0 to 禁用."

#: src/epggrab.c:437
msgid ""
"Writes the current in-memory EPG database to disk shortly after an xmltv "
"import has completed, so should a crash/unexpected shutdown occur EPG data "
"is saved (re-read on next startup)."
msgstr ""
"Writes the 当前 in-memory EPG database to disk shortly after an xmltv import "
"has completed, so should a crash/unexpected shutdown occur EPG 数据 is saved "
"(re-read on 下一个 startup)."

